items.title: Awesome Zsh Plugins
items.content_text:
### Themes / [superconsole](https://github.com/alexchmykhalo/superconsole) - Windows-only

*   [gal (⭐3)](https://github.com/x6r/gal) - Minimalist theme based on [gallois (⭐180k)](https://github.com/ohmyzsh/ohmyzsh/commits/master/themes/gallois.zsh-theme).
*   [headline (⭐300)](https://github.com/Moarram/headline) - A responsive ZSH theme featuring Git status information and a colored line above the prompt.
items.content_html:
Themes / superconsole - Windows-only

  • gal (⭐3) - Minimalist theme based on gallois (⭐180k).
